# Cloud Run Deployment

## Project Configuration

- **GCP Project:** knockoff-bot-demo
- **Service:** taloo-agent
- **Region:** europe-west1
- **URL:** https://taloo-agent-182581851450.europe-west1.run.app

## Deploy Command

```bash
gcloud run deploy taloo-agent --source . --region europe-west1 --allow-unauthenticated
```

This builds from the Dockerfile and deploys automatically.

## Verify Deployment

```bash
curl https://taloo-agent-182581851450.europe-west1.run.app/health
```

## Troubleshooting

If `gcloud` is not found, the SDK path is configured in `~/.zshrc`:

```bash
export CLOUDSDK_PYTHON=/opt/homebrew/bin/python3
export PATH="/opt/homebrew/share/google-cloud-sdk/bin:$PATH"
```
